Global Muscle-Building Protein Powder Market Insights
Muscle-Building Protein Powder Market size was valued at USD 18 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 30 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Muscle-Building Protein Powder Market Overview
The global muscle-building protein powder market is poised for significant growth, with a projected market value of USD 10.5 billion by 2027, expanding at a CAGR of 8.4% from 2023 to 2027. Increasing awareness about fitness and health, rising disposable incomes, and a growing demand for plant-based protein sources are some of the key factors contributing to market growth. The market is largely driven by the popularity of gym culture and the increasing focus on maintaining a healthy lifestyle among consumers of various age groups. With the surge in demand for personalized nutrition and supplements, the muscle-building protein powder market is expanding rapidly across regions.

